1
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:01,960
<i>I am 40 years old.</i>

2
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:06,680
<i>Normally at this age
in one's life, there comes a big twist.</i>

3
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,520
<i>There came a twist even in my life.</i>

4
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:11,040
<i>I mean, really big.</i>

5
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:13,520
<i>One that changed my life.</i>

6
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:21,160
<i>Actually, let's start
at the very beginning.</i>

7
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:32,280
<i>Since I was a kid I have been living
in this house with my</i>

8
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:34,520
<i>grandpa, grandma, mother and father.</i>

9
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:37,520
<i>My parents passed away when
I was eight years old.</i>

10
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:40,360
<i>My grandparents took care
of my upbringing.</i>

11
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:43,040
<i>When I was a child
I was very cute.</i>

12
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,400
<i>People would pull my cheeks and say...</i>

13
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,600
So sweet!

14
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:50,760
{\an8}<i>And this sweetness was even running
in my grandpa's business.</i>

15
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,600
{\an8}<i>Y. Y. Confectioners</i>

16
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:55,760
{\an8}<i>In Mumbai, the outlets of our shop
surpassed the greenery.</i>

17
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:58,400
{\an8}Please pack samosas
and half a kilo of <i>Jalebis</i>, brother.

18
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,520
Brother!

19
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,840
Y. Y. Confectioners!

20
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:07,160
{\an8}<i>My grandpa always interfered
in my love life.</i>

21
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,919
<i>At times he would call</i>

22
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:12,200
{\an8}<i>and at times he himself
would show up in person.</i>

23
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:16,160
{\an8}<i>I never had a relationship
so, clearly marriage was out of question.</i>

24
