{\an8}Did you see, Rahul?
Sachin plays so amazingly.

26
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:25,440
{\an8}<i>Though my grandpa was a die hard fan
of Sachin Tendulkar...</i>

27
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:28,640
{\an8}<i>he never applied the word "die"
in his life.</i>

28
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:31,480
<i>Time passed on but he did not.</i>

29
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,760
<i>All my relatives settled abroad.</i>

30
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,760
<i>And then, it was 2013.</i>

31
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,600
{\an8}<i>My grandpa's 100th birthday!</i>

32
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:42,960
{\an8}<i>All of my relatives gathered and,
