Yes, go ahead and open it.

69
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,600
{\an8}Why is he playing like this?

70
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:34,480
{\an8}Grandpa, we have already seen
an amazing plot in Panjim.

71
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:37,360
{\an8}Grandpa, can we go with Rahul
to finalize the plot?

72
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,040
- Go!
- Okay.

73
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:42,720
{\an8}Come on, Sachin!
Hit it beyond the boundary!

74
