78
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,640
Grandpa!

79
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:22,760
<i>Both grandpa and Sachin
were knocked out at 99!</i>

80
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,120
<i>It was a strange feeling.</i>

81
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:30,200
<i>But then I read that...</i>

82
