85
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:44,000
{\an8}<i>After all, grandpa lived since the era of
All India Radio to the advent of Twitter.</i>

86
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,960
<i>He lived a good life.</i>

87
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,840
<i>That's it!</i>

88
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,120
<i>At that very moment...</i>

89
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,680
<i>I had made a decision.</i>

90
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,720
