Chennai Express goes to Rameshwaram.

138
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,440
You did not understand.

139
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:40,320
Didn't I tell you that I want
to spend more time with grandpa?

140
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:43,520
